title: How to Paint - Neave Blacktalon
description:
Neave Blacktalon is as swift as lightning just as deadly, a single-minded hunter in Sigmar's service. 

In this video, we’ll be showing you how to paint Neave Blacktalon from the world of Warhammer: Age of Sigmar, and get her looking great on the gaming table in no time.

If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it: http://warhammer.me/3Vkojs6
